2013-01-22  Thomas Adam  <thomas@mvwm.org>
	* modules/MvwmWharf/MvwmWharf.c (FindLockMode):
	Fix missing deprecation of XKeycodeToKeysym() and mvwm_KeycodeToKeysym()

2013-01-22  Thomas Adam  <thomas@mvwm.org>
	* MvwmIconMan/debug.c (ConsoleMessage):
	* MvwmIconMan/functions.c (builtin_print):
	Comply with Debian's hardening rules.

	Debian's policy of what's considered "fit for purpose" for inclusion in
	its repositoy of packages says that all compiled programs must pass the
	following:

	CFLAGS="-I/usr/local/include -g -O2 -fstack-protector \
			--param=ssp-buffer-size=4 -Wformat -Werror=format-security" \
	LDFLAGS="-L/usr/local/lib"

	http://wiki.debian.org/HardeningWalkthrough

