2006-12-10  Viktor Griph  <griph(at)dd(dot)chalmers(dot)se>

	* MvwmWinList/MvwmWinList.c (ProcessMessage):
	Add buttons when items are added to make sure the lists are synced.

	* MvwmWinList/ButtonArray.c (AddButton,ButtonNew):
	Allow buttons to be created with NULL title.

