2006-04-26  Viktor Griph  <griph(at)dd(dot)chalmers(dot)se>

	* MvwmPager/MvwmPag
	* MvwmPager/MvwmPager.h (HandleScrollDone,list_string):
	* MvwmPager/x_pager.c (Scroll, do_scroll, HandleScrollDone):
	Changed to pixel operation. Scrolling is summed up before sent to
	mvwm to speed up multiple subsequent scrollings that take place faster
	than mvwm can change viewport.

