2003-08-07  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.h:
	* MvwmButtons/parse.c (ParseButton):
	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.c (DeadPipeCleanup):
	(My_FNextEvent):
	(swallow):
	(exec_swallow):
	(Loop):
	(SpawnSome):
	Used the new fsm lib to make MvwmButtons as a session manager for
	its swallowed apps when mvwm is runned under a session manager and
	MvwmButtons swallow some applications. This fixes swallowed apps
	multiplication after every save session/session restart.

