2002-11-24  Jason Weber  <baboon@imonk.com>

	* MvwmProxy/ConfigMvwmProxyDefaults:
	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.c (ProcessMessage):
	Twiddled with icon text placement rules.
	Added programmable Action options for Click1, Click2, ...
