		(which we're getting rid of).
	Changed all the *Command options to the Action syntax.
	Added the Circulate command that used core mvwm functions instead
		of internal Next/Prev.
	Commented out lots of code being phased out.
	Added Unmark Action to mirror Mark Action.

	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.1:
	Updated for Action commands and various formatting.

2002-11-20  Dominik Vogt  <dominik(dot)vogt(at)gmx(dot)de>

	* MvwmProxy/ConfigMvwmProxyDefaults:
	adjusted default functions

2002-11-20  Mikhael Goikhman  <migo@homemail.com>

	* MvwmDebug/MvwmGtkDebug.in:
	improved GUI, show event time, show window flags (as integers for now)

