2002-11-15  Jason Weber  <baboon@imonk.com>

	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.h:
	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.h:
	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.c:
	Fixed Next to really ignore windows on other desks.
	Added temp fix to use XFillRectangle vs. XClearWindow since the latter
	wasn't using the proper select colorset background color.
	Added .mvwm2rc configs for Width, Height, Separation, EnterSelect, and
	ProxyMove.
	Implemented the 'Prev" command.
	Extended Next/Prev commands to remember where they left off.

	* MvwmProxy/MvwmProxy.1:
	Filled out a lot of the man page

	* MvwmProxy/ConfigMvwmProxyDefaults:
	Added some defaults

