2002-01-28  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.c (ProcessMessage):
	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.h:
	Rewrite the non OLD_EXPOSE code and undef OLD_EXPOSE

	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.c (recursive_change_colorset):
	(swallow):
	(DeadPipeCleanup):
