2001-10-16  olicha  <olivier.chapuis@free.fr>

	* MvwmScript/Instruction.c:
	* MvwmScript/MvwmScript.1:
	* MvwmScript/script.y:
	* MvwmScript/scanner.l:
	* MvwmScript/script.c:
	* MvwmScript/scanner.c:
	New functions GetPid, Parse and SendMsgAndGet. The SendMsgAndGet
	function allows to extend MvwmScript with any programming language
	which can manipulate named pipe.

