1999-11-20  Dominik Vogt  <dominik(dot)vogt(at)gmx(dot)de>

	* MvwmIconMan/x.c (xevent_loop):
	workaround for a possible bug in XFree86; an EnterNotify event slipped
	into the loop body that was supposed to select only ConfigureNotify

	* MvwmCommand/MvwmCommandS.c:
	* MvwmCommand/MvwmCommand.c:
	fixed pipe names if DISPLAY is 'unix:0.0' under X, but ':0.0' on the
	console, i.e. 'unix' is removed and thus the hostname is used

	* MvwmIconMan/xmanager.c (clear_empty_region):
	fixed a minor redrawing bug when the width of the manager was not a
	multiple of the button width

	* MvwmWinList/MvwmWinList.c (AdjustWindow):
	fixed picture width calculation
	(ProcessMessage):
	mini icon changes change the window size too

	* MvwmPager/x_pager.c (SwitchToDeskAndPage):
	workaround for buggy XFree86

	* MvwmIconMan/functions.c:
	-Wall fix

