	* MvwmPager/*: new option *MvwmPagerWindow3dBorders set the pager
	mini windows to 3d if *MvwmPagerWindowColorsets is specified.
	*MvwmPagerWindowBorderWidth sets the minimum mini window size, the
	default of 1 gives the original size of 3x3.

