1999-05-12  Paul D. Smith  <psmith@gnu.org>

	* MvwmGtk/Makefile.am (INCLUDES): We appear to be standardizing on
	having modules use #include <libs/Module.h>, etc., rather than
	#include <Module.h>.  So, we need to add -I$(top_srcdir) to the
	includes list, not -I$(top_srcdir)/libs.  The latter won't work if
	you build outside of the distribution directory.

	* MvwmEvent/MvwmEvent.c (execute_event): free(buf) needs to go
	inside the if statement.

1999-05-12  Matthias Clasen  <clasen@mathematik.uni-freiburg.de>

	* MvwmPager/x_pager.c (DispatchEvent): fix desk name highlighting
	when switching desks with mouse button 3.

1999-05-11  Matthias Clasen  <clasen@mathematik.uni-freiburg.de>

	* MvwmEvent/MvwmEvent.c (event_table): bring in sync with
	list of events in Module.h, change the parsing of
	*MvwmEvent lines to treat everything after the event type
	as action.

