	geometry and mini-icon now and knows the options
	"NoGeometry", "NoMiniIcon", "Desk n", "CurrentDesk",
	"UseIconName", "Icons/NoIcons/OnlyIcons",
	"Sticky/NoSticky/OnlySticky", "Normal/NoNormal/OnlyNormal".

