	integer.

	* MvwmScroll/GrabWindow.c: include libs/Picture.h for prototype of
	InitPictureCMap.

Sun Apr  4 03:42:35 1999  Steve Robbins  <steve@nyongwa.montreal.qc.ca>

	* MvwmWinList/MvwmWinList.c: removed some includes.

	* MvwmWinList/MvwmWinList.h: move X11 includes from MvwmWinList.c
	into this file; protect against multiple inclusion.

	* MvwmWinList/List.c:
	* MvwmWinList/ButtonArray.c: include MvwmWinList.h for
	ConsoleMessage() prototype.

	* MvwmWinList/List.h: add prototype for ItemDesk.

	* MvwmWinList/ButtonArray.h: add prototype for UpdateButtonDesk
	and RadioButton.

	* MvwmWinList/List.c (PrintList):
	* MvwmWinList/MvwmWinList.c (ErrorHandler): make string format
	agree with argument.

	* MvwmTaskBar/Start.h: add prototype for StartButtonParseConfig.

	* MvwmTaskBar/MvwmTaskBar.c (LoopOnEvents): add braces to avoid
	ambiguous `else'.

