	* MvwmButtons/output.c (SaveButtons): added braces to avoid
	ambiguous `else's.

	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.c (Slide): initialize variables `xstep',
	`ystep', `wstep', and `hstep'.

	* MvwmButtons/MvwmButtons.c (Slide): initialize variables `w' and
	`h'.

