	* MvwmEvent/ChangeLog: removed erroneously-created files.
	Entries folded into this ChangeLog.

Sat Apr  3 14:34:28 1999  Steve Robbins  <steve@nyongwa.montreal.qc.ca>

	* MvwmScript/scanner.l: define YY_NO_UNPUT to suppress defining
	useless function.

	* MvwmScript/types.h: add prototype for yylex().

	* MvwmScript/Instructions.c (ReceivFromScript):
	* MvwmScript/Widgets/List.c (DrawCellule): reformat and insert
	braces to avoid ambiguous `else'.

	* MvwmScript/Widgets/CheckBox.c (EvtMouseCheckBox):
	* MvwmPager/x_pager.c (MapBalloonWindow): initialize variables to
	placate gcc -Wall.

	* MvwmPager/MvwmPager.c:
	* MvwmPager/x_pager.c: removed unused variables.

	* MvwmPager/MvwmPager.c (main): `==' should be `='.

	* MvwmIconMan/xmanager.c (button_left): initialize variable `i'
	before use.

	* MvwmIconMan/xmanager.c: removed COMPILE_STANDALONE nonsense
	around include mvwm.h.

	* MvwmIconMan/x.c:
	* MvwmIconMan/winlist.c (check_win_complete): fix debugging printf
	arguments.

	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (parse_function_list): cast pointer to
	unsigned long for debugging printf.

	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (ParseKeyEntry): initialize variables
	`actionstring' and `keystring'.

	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (ParseMouseEntry):
	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (ParseKeyEntry): cast Action to char*
	for debugging printf.

	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (read_in_resources): initialize
	variable `binding'.

	* MvwmIconMan/readconfig.c (print_binding,print_bindings): wrapped
	inside #ifdef PRINT_DEBUG.

	* MvwmForm/ReadXServer.c (ReadXServer): initialize old_cursor,
	otherwise it might be used uninitialized.

	* MvwmPager/MvwmPager.c:
	* MvwmForm/MvwmForm.c: include <libs/ModParse.h> removed.

Sat Apr  3 11:52:29 1999  Steve Robbins  <steve@nyongwa.montreal.qc.ca>

	* MvwmEvent/MvwmEvent.c (config): use GetNextOption() rather than
	GetArgument()

	* MvwmGtk/MvwmGtk.c (parse_arguments): use GetNextOption() rather
	than GetArgument().

	* MvwmPager/MvwmPager.c (ParseOptions): change GetArgument() to
	SkipNTokens().

	* MvwmAnimate/MvwmAnimate.c(ParseConfigLine): use GetNextOption
	rather than GetArgument; remove include of ModParse.h.

